<section>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Login</h1>
    <h3>You now have two ways to login</h3>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <p class='lead'>
        Login with email and password<br><br>
        {{#bs-button onClick=(action "password") type='primary' size='lg'}}Email and Password{{/bs-button}}
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Important:</strong>If this is the first time using this approach, you'll need to create a new password by clicking the "Don't remember your password?" link and following those instructions.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-6'>
      <p class='lead'>
        Login with a MagicLink (no password required)<br><br>
        {{#bs-button onClick=(action "passwordless") type='primary' size='lg'}}Passwordless MagicLink{{/bs-button}}
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>DEPRECATION NOTICE:</strong>Please note that the "MagicLink" login method will be deactivated on or after March 1.  Please consider moving to the email/password login method at your earliest convenience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <small><strong>Welcome:</strong> Barberscore is now operational for all BHS members. Edit permissions are only available to quartet contacts (for quartet entry), or pre-defined Chapter Leaders (for chorus entry). Please refer to competitor tutorials and FAQ (below) for more information. All other members should be able to view information about the quartets and choruses to which you belong.</small>
</section>